Features of MYSQL
Scalability - provide required amount of storage space 
Security -protect our database
High Performance - it is very fast and accurate

Commands in MYSQL
Data Definition Language - commands like defining, altering, dropping the structure of databases and tables
Data Manipulation Language - used for inserting, updating, retriving, deleting data from database
Data Control Language - commands for managing user privileges and permissions within the database (grant and revoke)

Data Types in MYSQL
Numeric Types - integer, float, double and decimal
String Types - characters, strings, texts, binary data
Date and time types - date and time

Advantages of MYSQL
Reliability - stability and constitent performance
Cost Effective - as it is a open source, cost efficient for business
Community Support - lareg community for assisstance and resources


